Installation (for Ubuntu):
    * sudo aptitude install python2.7 python-setuptools python-imaging
    * sudo easy_install pip
    * sudo pip install virtualenv

    * download source code (automate using fabric and git)
    * create virtualenv
    * sudo aptitude python-psycopg2 / sudo aptitude install python-mysql
    * pip install requirements.txt
    * edit settings.py
    * make sure that propriate media directories (static/, media/) are writable
    * python manage.py syncdb --all
    * python manage.py migrate --fake

    * lighttpd or 'python manage.py runserver' for development purposes
